lead_paragraph: Roger Federer overcame a lingering sickness to hold off Grigor Dimitrov 6-4, 6-7 (4), 6-4 on Friday and take his title defense into the semifinals at the Brisbane International.

headline.print_headline: Defending Champion Federer Into Brisbane Semifinals
